HEADWORD: To-break
<hw>To-break"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>to-</ets> + <ets>break</ets>.]</ety> <def>To break completely; to
break in pieces.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

